msgstr "Which image formats can be optimized?"

msgid "JPEG, PNG, WebP, and GIF files are supported. Each format is compressed using the most effective algorithm for that format."
msgstr "JPEG, PNG, WebP, and GIF files are supported. Each format is compressed using the most effective algorithm for that format."

msgid "What quality setting should I use?"
msgstr "What quality setting should I use?"

msgid "85 is a good default that balances quality and file size. For web use, values between 70 and 85 typically give the best results. Use 90+ when quality is critical, such as for print assets."
msgstr "85 is a good default that balances quality and file size. For web use, values between 70 and 85 typically give the best results. Use 90+ when quality is critical, such as for print assets."

