msgstr "Image Optimization FAQ"

msgid "Use WebP output for the smallest file sizes when targeting modern web browsers."
msgstr "Use WebP output for the smallest file sizes when targeting modern web browsers."

msgid "Set a max width of 1920px for full-screen hero images to avoid serving oversized files."
msgstr "Set a max width of 1920px for full-screen hero images to avoid serving oversized files."

msgid "For thumbnails and previews, a quality of 70-75 is usually indistinguishable from the original."
msgstr "For thumbnails and previews, a quality of 70-75 is usually indistinguishable from the original."

